<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4581214>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8–15. C. algerinus from Tunisia. (8–12) Gonopods of male from 12 km S of Thala. (8) Lateral view. (9) Mesal view. (10) Posterior view. (11) Anterior view. (12) Anterior view of posterior gonopods. (13, 14) Gonopods of male from 7 km S of Ain Draham. (13) Lateral view (L, lamella). (14) Posterior view of anterior gonopods. (15) Vulvae of female (O, operculum; B, bursa). Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4581214/files/figure.png" .
